<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Programming</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container my-5">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">What is Programming?</h1>
        
        <p class="lead text-center">
            Programming is the process of designing and building an executable computer program to accomplish a specific computing task. 
            It involves writing code in various programming languages that computers can interpret and execute. 
            Programming is the foundation of modern technology, powering everything from web applications to machine learning algorithms.
        </p>

        <section class="mt-5">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Why is Programming Important?</h2>
            <p>
                In the digital age, programming is an essential skill that drives innovation and progress. 
                It allows us to automate tasks, solve complex problems, and create systems that enhance productivity and improve lives.
                From the apps on your smartphone to large-scale enterprise software, programming is the backbone of the digital world.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="mt-5">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Popular Programming Languages</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3 class="text-center">JavaScript</h3>
                    <p>
                        JavaScript is one of the most widely-used programming languages, primarily known for creating interactive and dynamic web content. 
                        It's the backbone of modern web development, powering everything from front-end user interfaces to server-side logic.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3 class="text-center">Python</h3>
                    <p>
                        Python is a versatile language with a simple syntax that is popular for web development, data analysis, and artificial intelligence. 
                        It is widely used by developers, data scientists, and machine learning engineers.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3 class="text-center">Java</h3>
                    <p>
                        Java is a powerful, object-oriented programming language that is used for building enterprise-grade applications, Android apps, and large-scale systems.
                        Its "write once, run anywhere" philosophy makes it a popular choice for cross-platform development.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
